<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Transfer on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/transfer/</link><description>Recent content in Transfer on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/transfer/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Linux rsync Connection Error — Sync Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/os/linux/linux-rsync-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/os/linux/linux-rsync-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="linux-rsync-connection-error"&gt;Linux: rsync: connection error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;rsync: connection error&lt;/code&gt; message means rsync failed to establish or maintain a connection to the remote host. This can happen when using rsync over SSH (the default method) or when running the rsync daemon. The error may appear as &lt;code&gt;rsync: connection refused&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;rsync: error in socket IO&lt;/code&gt;, or &lt;code&gt;rsync: failed to connect&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;rsync uses SSH as its default transport protocol for remote file transfers. When you run &lt;code&gt;rsync -avz source user@host:dest&lt;/code&gt;, rsync establishes an SSH connection and uses the rsync protocol over that connection. Connection errors indicate the SSH connection failed, the rsync daemon isn&amp;rsquo;t running, or network issues prevented communication.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] macOS AirDrop Error — 'Person' Could Not Be Received</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/os/macos/airdrop-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/os/macos/airdrop-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="airdrop-error--person-could-not-be-received"&gt;AirDrop Error — &amp;ldquo;Person&amp;rdquo; Could Not Be Received&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An AirDrop error occurs when your Mac cannot send or receive files to/from another Apple device over Wi-Fi and Bluetooth. Common messages include &amp;ldquo;&amp;lsquo;Person&amp;rsquo; could not be received,&amp;rdquo; &amp;ldquo;No People Nearby,&amp;rdquo; and &amp;ldquo;Waiting.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;AirDrop uses Bluetooth LE for discovery and peer-to-peer Wi-Fi for transfer. Both radios must be working, and both devices must be within range. AirDrop is supported from macOS Yosemite (10.10) onward.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Maven Could Not Transfer from Remote Repository</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/maven/maven-repository-error-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/maven/maven-repository-error-v2/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="maven-could-not-transfer-from-remote-repository"&gt;Maven Could Not Transfer from Remote Repository&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when Maven cannot download artifacts from a remote repository due to network issues, authentication problems, or repository misconfiguration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network connectivity issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Repository URL is incorrect or down&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proxy settings not configured&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SSL certificate issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Repository requires authentication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="check-repository-connectivity"&gt;Check Repository Connectivity&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;curl -I https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="configure-proxy-settings"&gt;Configure Proxy Settings&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;!-- ~/.m2/settings.xml --&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;proxies&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;proxy&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;id&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;http-proxy&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/id&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;active&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;true&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/active&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;protocol&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;http&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/protocol&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;host&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;proxy.example.com&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/host&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;port&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;8080&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/port&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/proxy&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/proxies&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="skip-ssl-verification-temporary"&gt;Skip SSL Verification (Temporary)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mvn clean install -Dmaven.wagon.http.ssl.insecure&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;true
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="add-repository-with-authentication"&gt;Add Repository with Authentication&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;repositories&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;repository&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;id&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;private-repo&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/id&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;url&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;https://repo.example.com/releases&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/url&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/repository&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/repositories&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;!-- ~/.m2/settings.xml --&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;servers&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;server&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;id&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;private-repo&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/id&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;username&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;${env.REPO_USER}&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/username&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;password&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;${env.REPO_PASS}&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/password&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/server&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/servers&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="force-update-snapshots"&gt;Force Update Snapshots&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mvn clean install -U
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="use-offline-mode-for-local-cache"&gt;Use Offline Mode for Local Cache&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mvn clean install -o
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;[ERROR] Could not transfer artifact com.example:lib:jar:1.0.0
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; from/to central (https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; Transfer failed for https://repo.maven.apache.org/...
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; Connection timed out (ConnectException)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/maven/maven-dependency-error/"&gt;Maven Dependency Error&lt;/a&gt; — artifact not found&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/maven/maven-repository-error/"&gt;Maven Repository Error&lt;/a&gt; — repository connection failure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/maven/maven-wrapper-error/"&gt;Maven Wrapper Error&lt;/a&gt; — wrapper download failure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>